{{Infobox football biography |name = Khassa Camara |image = |image_size = |caption = |fullname = |birth_date = {{birth date and age|1992|10|22|df=y}} |birth_place = [[Châtenay-Malabry]], France |height = {{height|m=1.75}}<ref name = "NFT"/> |position = [[Midfielder#Defensive midfielder|Defensive midfielder]] |currentclub = [[Xanthi F.C.|Xanthi]] |clubnumber = 8 |youthyears1 = |youthclubs1 = |years1 = 2010–2014 |clubs1 = [[Troyes AC|Troyes B]] |caps1 = 49 |goals1 = 7 |years2 = 2012–2015 |clubs2 = [[Troyes AC|Troyes]] |caps2 = 11 |goals2 = 0 |years3 = 2014–2015 |clubs3 = → [[US Boulogne|Boulogne]] (loan) |caps3 = 9 |goals3 = 0 |years4 = 2015–2016 |clubs4 = [[Ergotelis F.C.|Ergotelis]] |caps4 = 7 |goals4 = 0 |years5 = 2016– |clubs5 = [[Xanthi F.C.|Xanthi]] |caps5 = 40 |goals5 = 0 |nationalyears1 = 2013– |nationalteam1 = [[Mauritania national football team|Mauritania]] |nationalcaps1 = 27 |nationalgoals1 = 1 |club-update = 23:25, 8 July 2018 (UTC) |ntupdate = 09:50, 31 August 2017 (UTC) }}
'''Khassa Camara''' (born 22 October 1992) is a Mauritanian international [[association football|footballer]] who plays for Greek club [[Xanthi F.C.|Xanthi]], as a [[Midfielder#Defensive midfielder|defensive midfielder]].
==Career== Born in [[Châtenay-Malabry]], France, Camara has played club football for [[Troyes AC|Troyes]] and [[US Boulogne|Boulogne]].<ref name = "NFT">{{cite web |url=http://www.national-football-teams.com/player/53638.html |title=Player profile |website=National-Football-Teams.com |accessdate=9 August 2015}}</ref><ref>{{Soccerway|khassa-camara/196787|accessdate=9 August 2015}}</ref> On 9 September 2015 he signed a two-year contract with Greek club [[Ergotelis F.C.|Ergotelis]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Ergotelis FC|title=Στον Εργοτέλη ο Khassa Camara (Greek) |url=http://www.ergotelis.gr/gr/anakoinoseis/ston-ergoteli-o-khassa-camara-5980|date=9 September 2015}}</ref> After legally filing for his contract with [[Ergotelis F.C.|Ergotelis]] to be terminated due to unpaid wages, he signed a six-month contract with top-level club [[Xanthi F.C.|Xanthi]] in January 2016.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=sport24.gr|title=Ανακοίνωσε Καμαρά η Ξάνθη, προς Κύπρο ο Ράνος (Greek) |url=http://www.sport24.gr/football/omades/SkodaXanthi/anakoinwse-kamara-h-ksanthh.3857226.html|date=12 January 2016}}</ref>
He made his international debut for [[Mauritania national football team|Mauritania]] in 2013.<ref name = "NFT"/>
