'''Liga Artzit''' ({{lang-he|ליגה ארצית}}. ''Artzit'') is the third tier level league of [[basketball]] competition in [[Israel]]. It is the league level that is below the second tier level [[Liga Leumit (basketball)|Liga Leumit]].
==League system== The league contains 12 clubs (in two districts), which compete in a home-and-away [[Round-robin tournament|round-robin]]. At the end of the season, the first team from each district (South/North) is promoted to the '''Liga Leumit'''.
The two teams that finish at the bottom of the table are relegated to the fourth tier, [[Liga Alef (basketball)|Liga Alef]].
