==World Disabled Swimmers of the Year==
{{also|Paralympic swimming|Best Female Athlete with a Disability ESPY Award}}
This award was created in 2003, and then was not awarded in 2004.<ref name="list"/> The award has been won by American swimmers six times, Brazilian and Australian swimmers four times, and Canadian swimmers twice.

